Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下还要洗被子  晾晒  淘米…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  花再不上肥的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛夷花已经盛开了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不抓紧不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果侑子小姐回来看见这些事都没做好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:01:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  侑子小姐现在出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那个  你不是来找侑子小姐的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为觉得你很有趣的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不知不觉的就过来了  不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的住所哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这里是家店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗？是怎么样的店呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…像是…像是什么都有的店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在帮这里的店主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打理店业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  学生还真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害你停下手边的事  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话  电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日  电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了  知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  这边似乎有点混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我还没办法回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难得想烤地瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦～我想吃烤地瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿也想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天再烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要马上趁热吃才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  明天我也回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说  我会有一段时间不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  这段时间你就可以休息了  不用过来打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会带礼物给你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真真真…的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵  不喜欢吃棉花糖啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说「不喜欢吃」  不如说「并不太清楚感觉」？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  那种轻飘飘的  粘糊糊的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不可思议物体一般的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  我知道我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  棉花糖真的是从棉花糖树上取得的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs22}（marshmallow，药属葵蜜饯，是从淡红色立葵的根部\N取得的粘液里加入蛋白、砂糖调味后得到的药用食品）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日对此了解的这么清楚呢  好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵的微笑好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有顾得过来作白色情人节的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那完全没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  没关系的～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  听见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百目鬼同学要去弓道社练习？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近都那么的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为离大会很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以再去加油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  小葵要去替百目鬼加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么难缠啊  她因为工作出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊  有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管狐怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在侑子小姐店里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在烟管里头睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好随身带着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  真是个莫名其妙的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是关系很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百目鬼和四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是搞不懂百目鬼那奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最不明白的是为什么他还那么受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你走路的时候表情千变万化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象心情很愉快的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  我并不觉得很愉快…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放学了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是早呢！你不参加社团的活动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是回家社
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为要打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过暂时休假了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否稍微陪我一下呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的地方可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想像这样  喝喝看罐装咖啡的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不会  并没有这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  你脸上都表现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直…很想和我的孩子这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在散步的时候  在放学回家的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微在顺路的时候说  「今天是个特别的日子」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  他很久以前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果长大的话  或许就是个像你一样的好孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在我实现了梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并…并没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还能再见的话  我想跟你聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…如果我…可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的孩子在小时候就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你们约好再见面了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  回去的时候想再聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位女士一定很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和四月一日在一起非常的愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是你和百目鬼同学说漫才的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs22}（漫才类似于中国的对口相声，兴起于日本关西）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我我我…我们哪有在说漫才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是在发呆和吐槽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;145;20;0,{\a6\fs22}关于{\fe128\fn麗流隷書\fs20}ボケ{\r\fs22}和{\fe128\fn麗流隷書\fs20}ツッコミ{\r\fs22}的翻译方法，一种是发呆役{\fe128\fn麗流隷書\fs20}(ボケ){\r\fs22}\N和吐槽役{\fe128\fn麗流隷書\fs20}(ツッコミ){\r\fs22}，同时可以用作动词“发呆”和“吐槽”；\N另一种是「傻角」{\fe128\fn麗流隷書\fs20}(ボケ){\r\fs22}和「捉角」{\fe128\fn麗流隷書\fs20}(ツッコミ){\r\fs22}」，\N「傻角」说一些蠢话，「捉角」便抓住这些蠢话，或拍打「傻角」脑袋，\N或教训、劝告其一番。其意义与第一种翻译法相同。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来发呆和吐槽的分别各是哪个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  四月一日是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到这个  百目鬼同学似乎很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还说不能一起吃便当
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  似乎就连午休的时间都要拿来练习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得四月一日亲自做的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  亲自做的话也不是那么辛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是刚刚有些做的辛苦了  完全没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是说你  是说百目鬼同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  班上弓道社的同学说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次大会或许能优胜也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他很拼命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是  那个家伙一个人的努力  和是否能得到优胜没什么关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为百目鬼同学是社里最厉害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  上次的我们去加油的大会  百目鬼同学就很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  小葵你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  对百目鬼…是不是…喜…喜…喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  上课铃响了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得收拾一下回教室才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要笑成那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我觉得你很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说都是不中用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢那个叫「小葵」的女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那那那那  那个啊…该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小葵在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的情绪都会像这个样子  高涨起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小葵能喜欢上四月一日的话  就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多  天色也越来越暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不回去的话  家人会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我一个人住所以没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老家很远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我的父母已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问了多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是多么久之前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去心爱的人这件事都会让人永远忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远都觉得寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得  舌头不应该被烫到的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是便当  味增饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢作菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果不嫌弃的话  下次换换口味也说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  如果给您麻烦的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常…非常的高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对我来说她是店主好呢  还是伟大的呢  任性的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  但有事干就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想和朋友去玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得能和你聊天很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也特别的高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再做些什么吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要您想吃的话  做什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…逞强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是马拉松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点郁闷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？四月一日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:15:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  好像感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你的脸色好差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是去保健室休息下为好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  不是什么大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在上体育课的时候晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是百目鬼同学把四月一日送到保健室来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我去叫老师来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:16:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我想应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有！没有！刚才什么都不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和魑魅魍魉有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我最近都没有遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那又怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的感冒连笨蛋都会被感染
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管狐如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好随身带着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近都没到侑子小姐店里去过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最…最近会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没必要怀疑这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎有点头晕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐一下会好些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有上体育课
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象太勉强你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  罐装咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  坐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象并没有发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:18:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是让我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前  发烧的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和爸爸都会这样帮我量体温
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前喝罐装咖啡  是实现了您的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  能这样  非常的高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  可是现在有体温计  而且我也可以自己量了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以看数字来判定是否生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不需要介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还是先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  先绕到侑子小姐那去看下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是四月一日  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见不见  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐还没有回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什么麻烦的事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见  四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个哦  还是不能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象很麻烦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧  遇到了各种各样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明和你说过要小心的  果然又发生了什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「发生了什么事」  什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身体不舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到那个女的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日  怎么了？…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.34,0:23:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离别  不知道哪一天会造访
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却明白总有一天会造访
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了最重要的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不想失去的某个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.39,0:23:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚美的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.19,0:23:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清那个结果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出选择的  是你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.99,0:24:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 ×××HOLiC
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.28,0:24:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望  让我来实现吧
